Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: The level of loans granted can not exceed the stock of tokens. Tokens participate in p2p lending and the bank does not take any risks acting as an intermediary between clients. In loans from the bank to customers, we use a risk hedging system, opening on the market simultaneously purchase and sale transactions for the amount of credit in the crypto currency, to protect the bank from losses associated with a decrease in price. It does not matter if the Crypto currency is growing or falling, we fixed its value at the time of issue.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: This looks somewhat interesting, and a team with expereince in the field and already operating close related businesses provides some kind of safety feel for investors, but I do need some questions answered first.  What is the point of MCB token within ecosystem other than discounts for services? If your fees are already low its not like you going to earn a lot cutting those fees, so holding tokens for that looks kinda pointless. Only real thing there is deposits rates increase, but holding volotile token just to make 2% more on deposits doesn't sound so good, unless your deposit i much larger than amount of tokens you owe. What is really a reason to buy your token when you can access all bank services without it?  Since your token is utility token bank profits are not going to be distributed amongst holders? Or will there be another mechanism to distribute profits? Will it be tied to ammount of tokens you hold or to your total stake in all currencies combined that you deposit to the project?  And last one, how is your token going to appreciate value? Whats in it for investors other than general crypto volatility?

With MyCryptoBank it will be possible to create deposits, receive loans and credits. The bank will create an infrastructure which will allow setting acquiring and merchants for goods payment for companies and online services. Clients will be able to receive bank cards and with the help of it they will take available funds through any ATM in the world and also pay in shops, restaurants etc. For client convenience, the bank plans to install ATM and crypto ATM, assisting in making operations on cryptocurrency purchase and cash receipt with minimum fees.

Author: yuvadeep
Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: In this modern world, everybody shows their interest towards digital money where the value is very high in the market. Internet digital currency helps people to access the bank accounts to their funds. Thus, these allow cheap and fast transfers of funds without any restrictions and limitations. MyCryptoBank provides services to customers and they access with the help of smartphones and debit cards. MyCryptoBank is an online bank, its responsibility is to allow users to register in the electronic bank system. Where users can perform all the bank operations, payment processing, debit cards, credit cards and invest in cheap products etc. Therefore, based on the blockchain technology MyCryptoBank provides all the services to the clients where bank services help in banking operations.  MyCryptoBank is a multi-functional modern banking platform which can be used for all the banking services,  it is a hybrid system which combines digital and traditional currencies. A digital currency plays an important role and performs operations faster and cheaper. MyCryptoBank is totally a digital bank, which can be available at any time throughout the world. Therefore, without taking the help of department in bank and front office, it totally depends on new digital technologies. However, MycryptoBank will be one of the most low-priced banks in the world with a valuable rank.  MyCryptoBank solves all the problems; it will be the first bank of its kind in the crypto community. Thus, helps clients to send and receive funds in the form of cryptocurrencies and fiat currency. As a result, both the exchange of cryptocurrencies and fiat money takes place within the bank. MyCryptoBank will help in create deposits, customer to find goods or services before payment, and receive loans in the form of fiat currency and cryptocurrencies.

Like a traditional contract, smart-contract defines rules of agreement and penalties for its performance. However, the most important thing is that this smart-contract automatically fulfills the compliance with obligations.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: One of the most powerful and evident advantages of our project is the well-established technological base, making possible the most efficient project development, avoiding the invariable non-optimal solutions. The 2nd prominent advantage of the project is the well-established user database of MyCryptoBank’s group of companies. These people are potential users of MyCryptoBank financial services. The 3rd project competitive advantage is MyCryptoBank’s business model. The major feature of the business model is separation of licensing and service of business units of the financial agent for operations with crypto currencies and the bank. Apart from the above, the speed and the simplicity of transaction banking based on modern technologies optimize the interbanking management and give efficient cost cutting.

Author: _mycryptobank_

Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: MyCryptoBank Pre-ICO starts on July 16! MyCryptoBank (https://mycryptobank.io) This is a traditional online bank that will provide all the banking services for its customers, as well as working with crypto currency (transfers, exchange of loans, loans, deposits and other services) We are focused on creating some ready-made solutions before the launch of our ICO. For example, we already have the following solutions: 1. We have developed our own crypto terminals (ATM crypto) that allow you to buy crypto-currencies for cash. (https://youtu.be/gVDvezfnCHU) 2. We have created crypto-exchange (https://mycryptobank.1bit.online) 3. we have a forex trading terminal and have a contract with a liquidity provider 4. We received 2 licenses for working with crypto-currencies + Lei (https://mtr.mkm.ee/taotluse_tulemus/485359 and https://mtr.mkm.ee/taotluse_tulemus/485362) 5. We met in the Philippines with the head of the special economic zone and the license for work with the crypto currency. https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:6422112560421621760 You can visit our site https://mycryptobank.io

Author: MyCryptoBank
Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: We have written about this in whitepaper p.5.5.1 MyCryptoBank plans to organize granting of credits for bank clients on security of their cryptocurrencies. Based on credits, the Bank will charge a one-time fee and also take the credited party's cryptocurrency as security for the term of the credit given. MyCryptoBank will take in the security of the most popular top-10 (BTC, ETH etc.) cryptocurrencies and also our MCB token. The volume of credit will not exceed 70% of the commercial value. To protect itself from security devaluation, MyCryptoBank will integrate a hedging scheme, where purchase / sale positions. In case of security price falls below 50% of the credit price, our cryptobank has the right to complete the transaction and sell this security at the common rate. All these actions will allow MyCryptoBank creating positive liquidity and do not suffer losses from loss assets and market fluctuations.

Author: MyCryptoBank
Title: [ANN] [ICO] MYCRYPTOBANK.IO - CRYPTOBANK FOR CRYPTOCOMMUNITY (preICO 16/07/2018)
Body: I'll start with the fact that we will have 2 options for crediting 1. Loan from the bank to the client on the security of its crypto currency. Loan within a few minutes, the process will be automated. The size of the loan will depend on the amount of collateral the borrower pays (70% of the deposit of the crypto currency). % of the loan - 10%. The loan can be anonymous. Credits are available only to holders of at least 6 000 MCB tokens. 2. Loan from customer to customer (P2P). Issuance of a loan after the creditor confirms the borrower's application. Terms and terms are set individually by the lender and the borrower. The creditor is provided with the borrower's history of previously obtained loans. Credits are available only to holders of at least 6 000 MCB tokens. For investors, the main advantage will be access to all the bank's tools, depending on the number of possession of the tokens, the discount for services and increased cashback increases, as well as additional bonuses in the form of gadgets - payment rings, multi-digital cards and other serices. Due to the fact that the number of tokens is limited and depending on the status of the client in the system, the tokens are frozen for 160 days, the tokens available for sale on the market will decrease, and in connection with the growing popularity of using our service and the growing demand for tokens MCB - their price will increase.
